---------- change Error message ----------

got to ( lang -> en -> validation.php  )

1 - there are all Error message, we can find and change it .

2 - To make special validation in under page there are two function  

   1 - custom to write message

         'custom' => [
                'name' => [
                         'required' => 'Please Enter Your :attribute'     //  attribute  is a parameters
                 ],
         ],

   2 - attributes to change attribute's name

	 'attributes' => [
    	         'name' => 'Full Name',
  	 ],